This is a new file added to the readme-edits branch.
Washing machine instructions:

1. make sure washing machine is installed correctly:
  a. water intake is connected to the supply of cold water
  b. water outlet is connected to drains
  c. power is connected to mains
  d. drum locks are removed.
2. load drum with clothes, keeping half the drum empty. close.
3. power ON
4. choose setting
5. press start
6. wait for finish
7. open, take clothes out
8. leave door open to dry for a bit.
9. power off.
